## Endpoint

### Health Check

```
GET /health
```

Response `200`:
```json
{
  "status": "ok",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "timestamp": "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z"
}
```

{{#if hasAuth}}
### Autentikasi

```
POST /auth/register
```
Request:
```json
{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "secure-password",
  "displayName": "User Name"
}
```

```
POST /auth/login
```
Request:
```json
{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "secure-password"
}
```
Response `200`:
```json
{
  "token": "jwt-token-here",
  "expiresIn": 3600
}
```

