## Format Error Response

Semua error response mengikuti struktur ini:

```json
{
  "error": {
    "code": "VALIDATION_ERROR",
    "message": "Deskripsi yang bisa dibaca manusia",
    "details": []
  }
}
```

Kode error standar:
- `VALIDATION_ERROR` (400)
- `UNAUTHORIZED` (401)
- `FORBIDDEN` (403)
- `NOT_FOUND` (404)
- `CONFLICT` (409)
- `INTERNAL_ERROR` (500)

