## Pagination

Endpoint list menggunakan cursor-based atau offset-based pagination:

```
GET /api/[resource]?page=1&limit=20
```

Response mencakup:
```json
{
  "data": [],
  "pagination": {
    "page": 1,
    "limit": 20,
    "total": 100,
    "totalPages": 5
  }
}
```

